    <h2>The History of Cheese</h2>
    <p>Cheese dates back over 7,000 years, possibly discovered by accident when milk was stored in animal stomachs. Ancient civilizations from Mesopotamia to Egypt valued cheese for its taste and shelf life. It has since evolved into a symbol of culture and craftsmanship across the world.</p>
